node ER · ER · ⟦Godfrey, First Elden Lord:ER:42957f⟧

WHO   — Godfrey, First Elden Lord — Hoarah Loux, the warrior who was banished to return
WHAT  — The first Elden Lord — consort of Marika, father of Godwyn, Morgott, and Mohg, the chieftain warrior Hoarah Loux.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the cast  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — His banishment created the Tarnished themselves — and at the very end he stands as the last challenger before the Ring, fighting bare-handed as the warrior he always was.
HOW   — He fought Marika's wars with the lion Serosh chained to his back to leash his battle-lust — and when stripped of grace, was banished as the first Tarnished, to one day return.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The lion set aside, the lord set aside — what remains is the warrior, bare-handed, first and last.

